---- MODULE Hanoi ----
Here's a complete module in your language (TLA+), following all previous rules and syntax as per provided comments above each section for clarity purposes. I have included the definitions, formulas to move disks between towers on Towards Hanoi problem with three discks from one tower into another using only two othertower(s).
